pt; "><font face="宋体">二、变更信息</font></span></b><b></b></p><p class="p" style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; " align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; "><font face="宋体">1、本项目</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; "><font face="宋体">一</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; "><font face="宋体">标段至</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; "><font face="宋体">三</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; "><font face="宋体">标段原工程量清单中部分内容调整</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; "><font face="宋体">，请各投标人重新下载相关内容</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; "><font face="宋体">。</font></span></p><h2 style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">2、</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">本项目</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">一</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">标段至</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">三</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">标段原招标公告和招标文件中</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">：</font><font face="宋体">3.7 各投标人均可就本招标项目六个标段中任意一个标段或多个标段进行投标，但最多允许中标1个标段。若出现两个或两个以上标段同时被推荐为第一中标候选人，则只能选择标段顺序最靠前的作为中标人，同时无条件放弃其他标段的中标资格；</font></span></h2><h2 style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">现变更为：</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">3.7各投标人均可就本招标项目六个标段中任意一个标段或多个标段进行投标，但最多允许中标一个标段。若出现两个或两个以上标段中标人为同一投标人的情况，则此投标人只能选择标段顺序最靠前的标段作为中标标段，同时无条件放弃其他标段的中标资格。后续不再进行递补中标候选人。</font></span></h2><h2 style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">3、</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">招标文件中涉及到的内容做相应变更，其它内容不变，给各潜在投标人带来不便敬请谅解。</font></span></h2><p class="MsoNormal" style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; "><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">三、变更公告发布媒介</font></span></b><b></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; "><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">变更公告在《郑州市公共资源交易中心》、《郑州市公共资源交易中心荥阳分中心》、《中国招标投标公共服务平台》上发布。</font></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; "><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">四、其他补充</font></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; ">