LY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">）</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">方案基本满足客户要求，但内容表述不清晰、操作性不强，得</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">3</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">分；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">（</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">4</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">）</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">方案存在缺陷、内容粗糙、可行性一般，得</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">1</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">分；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; tab-stops: left blank 18.0000pt" align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">（</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">5</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">）</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">未提供者不得分。</font></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; WIDTH: 58.1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RI