商对采购人优惠承诺，提供技术支持服务，设备操作人员培训，操作手册讲解等具有实质性优惠承诺的，得2分；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; tab-stops: left blank 18.0000pt" align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">（</font><font face="宋体">3）供应商对采购人提出优惠承诺，不具有实质性优惠承诺的，得1分；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; tab-stops: left blank 18.0000pt" align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">（</font><font face="宋体">4）未提供不得分。</font></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">2)原竞争性磋商文件“第五章 采购需求”</font></span></p><h1 style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; " align="center"><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">第五章</font> &nbsp;</span></b><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">采购需求</font></span></b><b></b></h1><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; "><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">附件</font><font face="宋体">1：</font></span></b><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">DN(15-25)水流量检定装置相关要求</font></span></b><b></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">一、检测设备总体要求：</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">1、生产企</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">业提供的检测设备的配置及附属设备应是国内同行业最先进的，自动化程度较高的；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">2、生产企业所选用的零部件及配件应是知名品牌原厂生产，并提供所有零配件型号及详单。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">3、生产企业应在行业内具有独特专利和独立研发能力，具备售后保障能力。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">4</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">、对检测设备要求，能够按照检定规程检测：热量表、冷量表、热水水表、冷水水表。</font></span></p><p class="16" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">5</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">、生产企业应至少具有一项热能表检定装置相关发明专利，并附相应证书。</font></span></p><p class="16" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">6</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">、生产企业应至少具有五项热能表检定装置相关实用新型专利，并附相应证书。</font></span></p><p class="16" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">7</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">、生产企业应至少具有五项热能表检定装置相关计算机软件著作权，并附相应证</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">书。</font></span></p><p class="15" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">二、执行标准</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">JJG 225-2024</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">《热量表检定规程》</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">JJG 686-2015 &nbsp;《热水水表检定规程》</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">JJG</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; ">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">162-2019 </font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; ">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">《饮用冷水水表检定规程》</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">JJ</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; ">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">G643-2003</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">《标准表法流量标准装置》</font></span></p><p class="19" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">JJF</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; ">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">1030-2023 &nbsp;&nbsp;《温度校准用恒温槽技术性能测试规范》</font></span></p><p class="19" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">JJG164-2000 &nbsp;&nbsp;《液体流量标准装置》 </font></span></p><p class="19" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">JJF2281-2025 &nbsp;《热量表通信, 技术协议计量技术规范》</font></span></p><p class="19" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">CJ/T357-2010 &nbsp;&nbsp;《热量表检定装置》</font></span></p><p class="19" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">注：应满足上述规程, 或标准内对检定设备的要求及检定项目的要求，项目实施期间如遇标准、规程的更新，将执行现行最新、有效的版本。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">三、技术参数</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">1、流量范围：（0.0</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; ">05</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">～</font><font face="宋体">8）m³/h；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">2、试验内容：示值误差检定、密封性实验；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">3、试验方法：标准表法、质量法；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">4、适用口径：DN15-DN25；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">5、被检表数量： DN15 10只、DN20 10只、DN25 8</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">只；</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">（能够单块仪表进行检测）</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">6、流量检定系统扩展不确定度：质量法≤0.2%（k=2）；标准表法≤0.3%（k=2）；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">7、配对温度传感器标准装置：温度不确定度≤0.01℃（k=2）；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">8、被检表种类：热量表、冷量表、热水水表</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">、冷水水表</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">等；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">9、被检表采集方式：红外、脉冲、M-bus或摄像采集；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">10、水箱温场均匀性要求：水箱温场均匀性：≤±2℃；水箱应6面保温，</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">保温厚度</font><font face="宋体">≥</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">5cm；水箱从常温加热到50℃应在2h内;</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">水箱保温能力：</font><font face="宋体">10℃/天；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">单次测量水温波动：</font><font face="宋体">≤0.5℃；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">11、检表台架应具备防护罩，可防止热水意外喷溅导致操作人员烫伤，也可以提升检定管段的保温性能，防护罩应具备一键自动开合功能，带亚克力观察视窗。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">12、装置运行压力：（0.1～0.6）MPa连续可调；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">13、装置温度范围：（10～90）℃；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">14、流量稳定性：≤±0.5%；</font></span></p><p class="16" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">15、二等标准铂电阻温度计（至少两根）；电测仪表；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">16、四槽恒温槽，能具备同时检测三个温差点的能力，并配置水三相点装置核查标准铂电阻温度计的漂移。恒温槽温度波动度≤0.01℃/30min；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">温场均匀度：</font><font face="宋体">0.01℃；恒温槽工作区域最大垂直温差：≤0.01℃；恒温槽工作区域最大水平温差：≤0.01℃。</font></span></p><p class="16" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">17、水三相点装置一套。符合热量表检定规程所需求。</font></span></p><p class="19" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">水三相点装置设备应满足以下参数：</font></span></p><p class="19" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">①冻制设备参数：</font></span></p><div align="center"><table class="MsoNormalTable" style="BORDE