p" style="WORD-BREAK: break-all; TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; " align="center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">内置制冷机冷却</font><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; ">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><font face="宋体">电热管加热</font></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div align="center"><!--StartFragment--><p class="15" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">②水三相点瓶参数</font></span></p><p class="15" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">◎ 包含水三相点瓶放置支架</font></span></p><p class="15" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">◎ 外形尺寸(mm):</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">≥</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">60*450</font></span></p><p class="15" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">◎ 浸入深度：</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">≥</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">265mm</font></span></p><p class="15" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">◎ 封装材料：硅硼玻璃或石英</font></span></p><p class="15" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">◎ 水源：是经过精心多次蒸馏的海洋水</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><span style="">四、</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">电磁流量计：</font><font face="宋体">DN3、DN10、DN25各1台；国际一线品牌高精度电磁流量计，用于指示当前检测管道的瞬时流量值，量程范围覆盖所有检定流量点，电磁流量计支持瞬时流量输出功能。精度满足标准表法流量测量不确定度 ≤0.3%（k=2）。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><span style="">五、</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">电子秤：采用国际一线品牌高精度电子秤，数量不低于两台，且至少具备一台检定精度为</font><font face="宋体">6000e；称重容器位于工作水箱上方，预留电子秤检定空间，用于检秤时放置标准砝码。</font></span></p><p class="15" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">六、清洗仪器仪表</font></span></p><p class="15" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">配备一套，超声波热量表清洗装置。用来清洗使用中表，以备表内杂质污染设备或将设备损坏。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">软化水系统：具备</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">自来水软化或净水功能</font><font face="宋体">,消除水垢及杂物</font></span></p><p class="15" style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); "><font face="宋体">七、其他要求</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">1、检定装置检定介质：清洁水；进水口应有水过滤系统和水净化器；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">2、所使用的水泵、气泵和空气压缩机等应是静音设备；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">3、原始记录能够自动保存和调取，未经授权不能更改。可自动打印已检定合格水表证书，也可自动设置其他时间打印证书。证书包括编号、检定日期、有效期至、检定员、核验员、检定单位等信息。证书能够单独保存；（证书模版及格式与我单位使用部门对接）。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">4、检测设备具备漏电保护装置；检测设备应具有应急关停装置。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">5、实验室场地限制，宽不大于2.5米，高不大于2.8米。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">6、配备相应的一套桌椅。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">7、检测设备及其附属设备应具有使用说明书和产品合格证，检测设备</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">和其附属设备应有市级以上法定技术机构有效期内检定证书或校准证书。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">8、检测设备所配置的电脑应具备扩容性。内存为</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">≥</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">32G；</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">≥</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">2TB固态硬盘；独立</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">显卡；显示器为</font><font face="宋体">24寸以上。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">9、检测设备所有电器包含电磁流量计，控制器，电脑等应有防潮、防电磁辐射等措施。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">10、检测设备运输、进场、装卸、实验室改造、水电路改造、防静电地线等均由设备销售方负责实施。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">11、检测设备调试完毕后，应不少于10个工作日对检定人员进行培训考核。 </font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">12、生产企业提供售后服务保障不少于5年，免费对检测设备进行维护保养。并终身免费对软件升级。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">13、按照检定规程要求，单独适配检定软件，包含热量表、冷量表、热水表、冷水水表的相关检测软件。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">备注：其它未注明设备配置以检定规程要求为准。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21.1pt; "><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">变更为</font></span></b><b></b></p>, <p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="Calibri">1)</font><font face="宋体">综合部分</font></span></p><div align="center"><table class="MsoNormalTable" style="BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: medium none; WIDTH: 100%; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; BORDER-BOTTOM: medium none; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; " cellspacing="0" border="1"><tbody><tr><td style="BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; WIDTH: 42.7pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; " valign="middle" rowspan="3" width="56"><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; " align="center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">2.2.2（3））</font></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; WIDTH: 59.05pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; " valign="middle" rowspan="3" width="78"><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; " align="center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">综合部分（</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">20</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">分）</font></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; WIDTH: 58.1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; " valign="middle" width="77"><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; tab-stops: left blank 18.0000pt" align="center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">业绩（</font><font face="宋体">8分）</font></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; WIDTH: 266.25pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; " valign="middle" width="355"><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">自</font><font face="宋体">202</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">3</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">年</font><font face="宋体">1月1日（以合同签订时间为准）以来每提供1份</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">所投产品的</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">合同得</font><font face="宋体">2分，最多得8分。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">注</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">：需提供合同扫描件。不</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">符合要求的该项业绩不得分。</font></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; WIDTH: 58.1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; " valign="middle" width="77"><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; tab-stops: left blank 18.0000pt" align="center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">售后服务方案（</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">8</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">分）</font></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; WIDTH: 266.25pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; " valign="middle" width="355"><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; tab-stops: left blank 18.0000pt" align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">售后服务方案包括质保期内和质保期外售后服务方案，磋商小组根据售后服务方案的内容、形式（含维修人员组成）；免费维修时间；解决问题方案（含应急突发事件）；出现操作问题的响应时间等内容进行综合评审打分。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">（</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">1</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">）</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">方案科学合理、内容详细、完整、切实可行、针对性强、完全满足采购需求得</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">8</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">分；</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">（</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">2</font></span><span style="FON