51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; "><font face="宋体">、招标文件专用合同条款中未填写工程进度款支付条件，请明确。</font></span></p><p class="p" style="BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 22.2pt; "><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; "><font face="宋体">答复如下：</font></span></b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; "><font face="宋体">按工程进度付款，厂房主体结构建设至</font><font face="宋体">1层之日起7日内拨付完成工程量的80%，主体结构封顶之日起7日内拨付完成工程量的80%，二次结构完成之日起7日内拨付完成工程量的80%，工程竣工验收合格、承包人提交竣工结算报告，结算报告经政府财政结算中心审核后，7日内拨付财政结算总价的97%，剩余3%作为质量保证金。 </font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; ">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p class="p" style="BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 22.2pt; "><b style=""><span class="15" style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; "><font face="宋体">疑问</font><font face="宋体">2、</font></span></b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; "><font face="宋体">2025年2月24日一标段变更公告中招标范围发生变更，建筑面积由90000平方米变更为56827.62平方米，未见招标控制价相应调整，请明确。</font></span></p><p class="p" style="BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN: 0pt