 face="宋体">（</font><font face="宋体">2）是否专门面向中小企业：</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-STYLE: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">否</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; " align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">（</font><font face="宋体">3）落实政府采购政策需满足的资格要求：本项目非专门面向中小企业采购；本项目落实节约能源、保护环境、促进中小企业发展、促进残疾人就业等相关政府采购政策。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; " align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">（</font><font face="宋体">4）法人或者分公司的营业执照等证明文件（以分公司等不具有独立承担民事责任能力的其他组织名义参加的，须提供其总公司或所属法人机构的授权文件，可使用其总公司相关资质和资料）。具备履行合同所必需的设备和专业技术能力（提供相关设备和人员合同的证明材料，并提供承诺书）。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; " align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">2、磋商文件及其他相关内容同步变更。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; " align="justify"><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-STYLE: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">三、其他补充事宜</font></span></b><b></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: justif