体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">1</font></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; WIDTH: 406.55pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; " valign="top" width="542"><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">系统平台可实现全院药品统一管理，构建院内多个药品管理系统的药品管理统一平台：可实时获取院内病区智能药柜实时库存信息，药品转运信息及临床最终患者床边给药核对信息，支持对药品在院内整个流转全过程管理及查询数据汇总及统计分析，提供医院决策支持。</font></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; WIDTH: 25.5pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; " valign="middle" width="34"><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; " align="center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">2</font></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; WIDTH: 406.55pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; " valign="top" width="542"><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">HIS:与医院信息系统对接，同步科室信息/用户信息/患者信息/医嘱信息/药品信息/手术信息等。</font></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; WIDTH: 25.5pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; " valign="middle" width="34"><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIG