y: 宋体; ">二、更正信息</span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; "><b><span lang="EN-US" style="background: white; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; ">1</span></b><b><span style="background: white; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; ">、变更内容</span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; "><span style="background: white; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; ">“</span><b style=""><span style="color: black; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; ">二、申请人的资格要求：</span></b></p><p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph; "><span lang="EN-US" style="background: white; color: black; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; ">3.</span><span style="background: white; color: black; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; ">本项目的特定资格要求</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph; "><span style="background: white; color: black; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; ">（<span lang="EN-US">1</span>）在中华人民共和国境内注册，具有独立承担民事责任的能力，提供有效的企业法人营业执照或者其他组织等相关证明。供应商如果不是具备独立法人资格的分公司<span lang="EN-US">,</span>则须提供其具有独立法人资格的上级总<span lang="EN-US">(</span>母<span lang="EN-US">)</span>公司对其出具的有效授权；</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph; "><span style="background: white; color: black; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; ">（<span lang="EN-US">2</span>）供应商具有中国保险监督管理委员会颁发的《经营保险业务许可证》；</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; "><b><span style="background: white; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-