YLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">2</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">月</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">1</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">1日在《河南省政府采购网》、《焦作市公共资源交易中心网》发布了招标公告，现发布变更公告，内容如下：</span></span></p><p style="BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 29px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">一、项目信息：</span></span></p><p style="BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0px 0px 64px; LINE-HEIGHT: 29px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">项目名称：</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">亚投行紧急优惠贷款支持河南省暴雨洪涝灾害灾后恢复重建项目焦作子项目</span>-焦作市大沙河水毁修复工程勘察设计项目</span></p><p style="BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 29px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-STYLE: normal; LE