('濮阳市华龙区第五中学实验楼项目更正公告', 'GOV_PROCUREMENT', 'correction', 'service', '濮阳市华龙区第五中学', NULL, NULL, NULL, '河南省', '濮阳市', '市区', '河南省 濮阳市 市区', '<p class="p" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">濮阳市华龙区第五中学实验楼项目受濮阳市华龙区第五中学的委托，就濮阳市华龙区第五中学实验楼项目进行公开招标。于</font><font face="宋体">2021年</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">5</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">月</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">27</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">日在《中国招标投标公共服务平台》、《河南省电子招标投标公共服务平台》、《濮阳市公共资源交易平台》发布招标公告，现发布变更公告如下：</font></span></p><p class="p" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-WEIGHT: bold; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">一、</font></span></b><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-WEIGHT: bold; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">项目概况与招标范围</font></span></b><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-WEIGHT: bold; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">：</font></span></b><b></b></p><p class="p" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">1、项目名称：濮阳市华龙区第五中学实验楼项目</font></span></p><p class="p" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">2、项目编号：HLZB-2021-048</font></span></p><p class="p" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">3、建设地点：华龙区五中校园内；</font></span></p><p class="p" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">4、项目概况：建筑面积2300平方米，新建3层框架结构实验楼一栋；</font></span></p><p class="p" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">5、投资金额：约570万元；</font></span></p><p class="p" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">6、招标范围：施工图纸及工程量清单内所有内容；</font></span></p><p class="p" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">7、工期：240日历天</font></span></p><p class="p" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span styl