><b></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21.1pt; "><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; ">1、原招标文件</span></b><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; "><font face="宋体">第五章</font></span></b><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; "><font face="宋体">发包人要求中：</font></span></b><b></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">一、建设范围及内容：</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; ">1、项目建设地点：大营镇、原店镇、西张村镇、张湾乡、硖石乡、张汴乡、宫前乡、店子乡、观音堂镇、西李村乡、王家后乡、菜园乡、张茅乡等。</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; ">2、项目建设规模：拟建规模487.99公里，估算总投资31581.4万元，资金来源为财政资金。</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; ">3、该项目包含：“四好农村路”建设项目四块39个，建设内容包括路基、路面，配套设施有绿化、安保、标志标牌、路域整治等。</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21.1pt; "><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; "><font face="宋体">现变更为：</font></span></b><b></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">一、建设范围及内容：</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; ">1、项目建设地点：大营镇、原店镇、西张村镇、张湾乡、硖石乡、张汴乡、宫前乡、店子乡、观音堂镇、西李村乡、王家后乡、菜园乡、张茅乡等。</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; ">2、项目建设规模：拟建规模487.99公里，估算总投资31581.4万元，资金来源为财政资金。</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; ">3、该项目包含：“四好农村路”建设项目四块39个，建设内容包括路基、路面，配套设施有绿化、安保、标志标牌、路域整治等。</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; ">4、拟建规模：</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">（</font>1）环线一：五原-草庙-县城，路线长：38.856km。</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">五原</font>-草庙-县城环线工程</span></p><div align="center"><table class="MsoNormalTable" style="BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: medium none; WIDTH: 426.1pt; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; BORDER-BOTTOM: medium none; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; " cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody><tr style="HEIGHT: 28.35pt"><td style="BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; WIDTH: 36.5pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; " valign="middle" width="48"><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; " align="center"><span 