 1pt; COLOR: black; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; ">、原更正公告中保证金交款截止时间<span lang="EN-US">2020</span>年<span lang="EN-US">7</span>月<span lang="EN-US">23</span>日<span lang="EN-US">9</span>时<span lang="EN-US">00</span>分。</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.75pt; " align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,sans-serif; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; COLOR: black; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; ">现更正为：保证金交款截止时间<span lang="EN-US">2020</span>年<span lang="EN-US">8</span>月<span lang="EN-US">18</span>日<span lang="EN-US">9</span>时<span lang="EN-US">00</span>分。</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.75pt; " align="left"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,sans-serif; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; COLOR: #444444; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; ">4</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,sans-serif; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; COLOR: #444444; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; ">、原招标文件前附表<span lang="EN-US">10.2.1</span>及附录<span lang="EN-US">4</span>资格审查条件（人员最低要求）中投标人须提供备查的原件：企业法人营业执照（副本<span style="LETTER-SPACING: -2.25pt">）</span><span style="LETTER-SPACING: -0.75pt">、企业资质证书</span>（<span style="LETTER-SPACING: -0.75pt">副</span>本），证明企业业绩的中标通知书、合同协议书、交（竣）工报告（时间以交（竣<span style="LETTER-SPACING: -2.25pt">）</span>工报告日期为准<span style="LETTER-SPACING: -2.25pt">）</span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.75pt; TEXT-INDENT: 12pt; " align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,sans-serif; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; COLOR: #444444; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; ">注：以上所有要求（除营业执照、资质证书、安全生产许可证可提供原件或提供加盖投标人公章的复印件及资质证书查询信息）均须提供原件供评标委员会审验，未提供者，按废标处理。</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.75pt; TEXT-INDENT: 12pt; " align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,sans-serif; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; COLOR: #444444; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; ">现更正为：投标人须提供备查的原件：企业法人营业执照（副本<span style="LETTER-SPACING: -2.25pt">）</span>，证明企业业绩的中标通知书、合同协议书、交（竣）工报告（时间以交（竣<span style="LETTER-SPACING: -2.25pt">）</span>工报告日期为准<span style="LETTER-SPACING: -2.25pt">）</span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.75pt; TEXT-INDENT: 12pt; " align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,sans-serif; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; COLOR: #444444; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; ">注：以上所有要求（除资质证书可提供原件或提供加盖投标人公章的复印件）均须提供原件供评标委员会审验，未提供者，按废标处理。</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.75pt; " align="left"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,sans-serif; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; COLOR: #444444; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; ">5</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,sans-serif; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; COLOR: #444444; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; ">、原招标文件前附表<span lang="EN-US">7.7.1</span>中履约保证金：履约保证金（在合同签订前递交给招标人）</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.75pt; TEXT-INDENT: 11.25pt; " align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,sans-serif; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; COLOR: #444444; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; ">现更正为：（<span lang="EN-US">1</span>）履约保证金：按签约合同价的<span lang="EN-US">10%</span>。根据《沁阳市人民政府关于印发沁阳市政府投资建设工程项目（政府采购项目）履约保证金管理办法（试行）的通知》（沁政【<span lang="EN-US">2017</span>】<span lang="EN-US">16</span>号）执行。中标公示期结束后<span lang="EN-US">15</span>天内交纳。</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.75pt; TEXT-INDENT: 11.25pt; " align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,sans-serif; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; COLOR: #444444; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; ">（<span lang="EN-US">2</span>）履约担保的形式：银行转账或保函</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.75pt; TEXT-INDENT: 11.25pt; " align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,sans-serif; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; COLOR: #444444; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; ">（<span lang="EN-US">3</span>）招标项目经验收合格后无息全额退还履约保证金。</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.75pt; TEXT-INDENT: 11.25pt; " align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,sans-serif; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; COLOR: #444444; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; ">备注：保函应由银行、保险公司、沁阳市诚信担保有限责任公司（市国资委下属）出具。</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.75pt; " align="left"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,sans-serif; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; COLOR: #444444; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; ">6</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,sans-serif; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; COLOR: #444444; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; ">、其它事项不变。</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.75pt; " align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,sans-serif; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; COLOR: #444444; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; ">三、本次招标联系事项</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.75pt; " align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,sans-serif; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; COLOR: #444444; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; ">招 标 人：沁阳市公路管理局</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.75pt; " align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,sans-serif; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; COLOR: #444444; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; BORDER-L