('濮阳市华龙区戚城小学室外配套工程流标公示', 'GOV_PROCUREMENT', 'correction', 'service', '濮阳市华龙区石化路第一小学', NULL, NULL, NULL, '河南省', '濮阳市', '市区', '河南省 濮阳市 市区', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; "><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; "><font face="宋体">一、</font></span></b><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; "><font face="宋体">项目概况与招标范围</font></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.85pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; ">1、</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; "><font face="宋体">项目名称：濮阳市华龙区戚城小学室外配套工程。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.85pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; ">2、</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; "><font face="宋体">招标编号：</font>HLZB-2020-047。</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.85pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; ">3</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; "><font face="宋体">、</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; "><font face="宋体">建设地点：该项目位于开州路与戚邑路交叉口东北角。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.85pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; ">4</span><span style