('羊山新区信钢嘉园东规划路新建工程变更公告', 'GOV_PROCUREMENT', 'correction', 'service', '羊山新区开发建设委员会', NULL, NULL, '2020-02-14 09:30:00', '河南省', '郑州市', '市区', '河南省 郑州市 市区', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">河南海隆工程咨询有限公司受羊山新区开发建设委员会的委托，对羊山新区信钢嘉园东规划路新建工程进行公开招标，已于</font>2019年1月20日在《河南省电子招标投标公共服务平台》、《信阳市公共资源交易网》上发布了招标公告。现对该项目发布变更公告：</span></p><p class="p" style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; " align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">一、项目名称：羊山新区信钢嘉园东规划路新建工程</font></span></p><p class="p" style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; " align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">二、招标编号：信建公开招标</font>SZ（2020）1号</span></p><p class="p" style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; " align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">三、原招标公告：</font></span></p><p class="p" style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; " align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; ">1、投标文件递交的截止时间：投标文件递交的截止时间（开标时间）为2020年2月14日9时30分。</span></p><p class="p" style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; " align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; ">2、开标地点：信阳市公共资源交易中心四楼第三开标厅。</span></p><p class="p" style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; " align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">现变更为：</font></span></p><p class="p" style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; " align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; ">1、投标文件递交的截止时间：投标文件递交的截止时间（开标时间）为2020年4月13日上午10时00分。</span></p><p class="p" style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; " align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; ">2、开标地点：信阳市公共资源交易中心四楼第一开标厅。</span></p><p class="p" style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; " align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">招标文件中相对应部分依照此变更做相应更改，其他内容不变</font></span></p><p class="p" style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; " align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">四、发布媒介：本次变更公告同时在《河南省电子招标投标公共服务平台》、《信阳市公共资源交易网》上发布。</font></span></p><p class="p" style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; " align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-STYLE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">五、联系方式</font></span></p><p class="p" style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; MARGIN: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; " align="justify"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51);