('信阳市集中供热一期工程管网施工及安装项目第三标段、第四标段流标公告', 'GOV_PROCUREMENT', 'correction', 'goods', '信阳热力有限公司', NULL, NULL, NULL, '河南省', '信阳市', '市区', '河南省 信阳市 市区', '<tbody><tr><td valign="top"><table width="100%"><tbody><tr><td height="10"></td></tr><tr height="22"><td align="center" style="font-size:18px;"><strong>信阳市集中供热一期工程管网施工及安装项目第三标段、第四标段流标公告</strong></td></tr><tr><td align="center" height="20"><font style="color:#333333; line-height:20px;"> 发布者：黄少侠&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 浏览次数：1525&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 发布时间：2019/8/15 </font></td></tr><tr><td height="5"></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0px 5px 5px 10px; line-height:22px; font-size:14px;" valign="top"><!--StartFragment--><p style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; " class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; " class="15"><font face="宋体">河南海隆工程咨询有限公司受信阳热力有限公司的委托，就信阳市集中供热一期工程管网施工及安装项目进行公开招标，现将第三标段、第四标段相关情况公示如下：</font></span></p><p style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; " class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; " class="15"><font face="宋体">一、项目名称及编号</font></span></p><p style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; " class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; " class="15">1.1项目名称：信阳市集中供热一期工程管网施工及安装项目</span></