; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; " class="15">2.2.招标公告时间：2019年6月26日至2019年7月2日</span></p><p style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; " class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; " class="15"><font face="宋体">三、流标情况说明：</font></span></p><p style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; " class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; " class="15"><font face="宋体">由于第三标段、第四标段中标单位放弃中标，招标人决定重新招标。因此第三标段、第四标段流标。</font></span></p><p style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; " class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; " class="15"><font face="宋体">四、联系事项：</font></span></p><p style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; " class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; " class="15"><font face="宋体">招标人：信阳热力有限公司</font></span></p><p style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; " class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; " class="15"><font face="宋体">地址：信阳市平桥区平安大道</font>1号</span></p><p style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; " class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; " class="15"><font face="宋体">联系人：杨先生</font></span></p><p style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; " class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; " class="15"><font face="宋体">联系电话：</font>0376-3616888</span></p><p style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; " class="MsoNormal" align="justify">&nbsp;</p><p style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; " class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; " class="15"><font face="宋体">招标代理机构：河南海隆工程咨询有限公司</font></span></p><p style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; " class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; " class="15"><font face="宋体">地址：郑州市郑东新区金水东路与心怡路交汇处雅宝东方国际广场</font>2号楼1306室</span></p><p style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; " class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; " class="15"><font face="宋体">联系人：吴女士</font></span></p><p style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; " class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); LETTER-SPACING: 0pt; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; " class="15"><font face="宋体">电话：</font>17737113681、0371-55894666</span></p><!--EndFragment--></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody>', '黄少侠', '2019-08-15 00:00:00', 1524, 0, 1, 0, NOW(), NOW()),
('固始县国机励志学校2019-2020学年度食堂管理服务政府采购项目招标文件变更公告', 'GOV_PROCUREMENT', 'correction', 'goods', '固始县教育体育局', NULL, NULL, '2019-08-16 08:30:00', '河南省', '信阳市', '固始县', '河南省 信阳市 固始县', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">一、项目名称：</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">固始县</font><font face="宋体">国机励志学校</font>2019-2020学年度食堂管理服务政府采购项目</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">二、项目编号：</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; ">G</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; ">CGZ-2019-093</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">三、首次公告日期及发布媒体：</font>2019年7月25日，</span><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">发布媒体：</font></span></b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">《河南省电子招标投标公共服务平台》、《</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">中国</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">政府采购网》、《河南省政府采购网》、</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">《全国公共资源交易平台（河南省</font>•固始县）》</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">。</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 36pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">四、原投标截止时间（投标文件递交截止时间）或响应文件提交截止时间：</font>2019年8月16日8时30分。</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 36pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">五、变更内容：</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; ">1、原采购信息内容：招标文件第二章 &nbsp;供应商须知及前附表中<font face="宋体">供应商须知</font><font face="宋体">正文</font>“25、定标程序&nbsp;&nbsp;25.2采购人在收到评标结果后5个工作日内，按照评标结果中推荐的中标候选人顺序确定中标人。”</span></p><p class="16" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; "><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; "><font face="宋体">变更为：</font></span></b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; ">“25、定标程序 </span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; ">25.2采购人在收到评标结果后5个工作日内，按照评标结果中推荐的中标候选人顺序确定排名在前的2名供应商为该项目的中标人，</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">一家供应商负责中学段建档立卡贫困生预计</font>2600人，资金约3848000.00元；另一家供应商负责小学段建档立卡贫困生预计，1900人，资金约2812000.00元，入围两家供应商具体如何分配，由学校根据两家企业的实际情况决定</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; ">”</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; ">2、原采购信息内容：招标文件<font face="宋体">第六章</font> &nbsp;<font face="宋体">评标办法中</font>“六、合同将授予符合招标文件要求，质量和服务相等且报价最低综合得分最高的供应商。”</span><b></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; "><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">变更为：</font></span></b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; ">“六、合同将授予符合招标文件要求，质量和服务相等且最终得</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">分最高和次高的</font>2名供应商。”</span></p><p class="16" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; ">3、原招标文件中的详细评审标准现变更为:详见附件1</span></p><p class="16" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; ">4、其他内容不变。</span></p><p class="16" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">六、联系方式</font></span></p><p class="16" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">采购人：固始县教育体育局</font></span></p><p class="16" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">地址：固始县蓼城大道南段</font></span></p><p class="16" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">联系人：王先生</font></span></p><p class="16" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">电话：</font>0376-3238123</span></p><p class="16" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "></p><p class="16" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体"></font></span>&nbsp;</p><p class="16" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">采购代理机构：</font><font face="宋体">河南海隆工程咨询有限公司</font></span></p><p class="16" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">地址：郑州市郑东新区金水东路与心怡路交汇处雅宝东方国际广场</font>2号楼1306室</span></p><p class="16" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">联系人：张女士</font></span></p><p class="16" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">电话：</font>17596999059、0371-55894666</span></p><p class="16" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; "></p><p class="16" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: right; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; " align="right"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">发布人：河南海隆工程咨询有限公司</font></span></p><p class="16" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: right; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; " align="right"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; "><font face="宋体">发布时间：</font>2019年8月1日</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; "><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><font face="宋体">附件：采购信息变更后的内容见附件</font></span></b><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; ">1</span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; "><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; "><img border="0" src="/admin/edit/sysimage/icon16/doc.gif"><a href="/uploadfile/20190801174802416.doc" target="_blank">附件1.doc</a></span></b><b></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; "><b></b></p>', '黄少侠', '2019-08-01 00:00:00', 1433, 0, 1, 0, NOW(), NOW()),
('潢川县城区及四办两区环卫保洁运营服务项目延期公告', 'GOV_PROCUREMENT', 'correction', 'goods', '潢川县城市管理局', NULL, NULL, NULL, '河南省', '信阳市', '潢川县', '河南省 信阳市 潢川县', '<p style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LETTER-SPACING: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial" align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">河南海隆工程咨询有限公司受潢川县城市管理局的委托，现就潢川县城区及四办两区环卫保洁运营服务项目进行公开招标，该项目于<span>2019</span>年<span>7</span>月<span>9</span>日在</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">《河南省电子招标投标公共服务平台》、《</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">中国</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">政府采购网》、《河南省政府采购网》、《信阳市公共资源交易网》</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">同时发布了招标公告，因需对招标文件内容进行澄清说明，现对本项目开标时间发布延期公告。</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LETTER-SPACING: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial" align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">一、项目名称：潢川县城区及四办两区环卫保洁运营服务项目</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LETTER-SPACING: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial" align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">招标编号：潢公采【<span>2019</span>】<span>036</span>号</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LETTER-SPACING: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial" align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">二、招标公告信息：</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LETTER-SPACING: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial" align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">原公告开标时间：<span>2019</span>年<span>8</span>月<span>2</span>日<span>09</span>时<span>30</span>分（北京时间）；</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LETTER-SPACING: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial" align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">原公告</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">投标文件递交的地点为：信阳市行政服务中心四楼第</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">五</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">开标厅（信阳市羊山新区新七大道与新十街交叉口）</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">。</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LETTER-SPACING: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial" align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">三、延期事项内容：</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LETTER-SPACING: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial" align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">现开标时间为：<span>2019</span>年<span>8</span>月<span>5</span>日<span>14</span>时<span>00</span>分（北京时间）；</span></p>