rmal; "><font face="宋体">。</font></span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; " class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; "><font face="宋体">原内容为：</font></span></b></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; " class="MsoNormal"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; "><font face="宋体">因第一中标候选人河南泽宇水利水电工程有限公司的项目经理不具备中标资格，故本标段顺延第二名为中标人。</font></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; " class="MsoNormal"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; "><font face="宋体">中标人</font></span><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; "><font face="宋体">：河南信越建设有限公司</font></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; " class="MsoNormal"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; "><font face="宋体">投标报价：</font></span><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; ">2318216.66</span><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; "><font face="宋体">元</font></span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; " class="MsoNormal"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; "><font face="宋体">项目经理：</font></span><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 