('固始县慈济高中实验楼及国机励志学校分校一期工程（景观）建设项目变更公告', 'CONSTRUCTION', 'correction', 'goods', '固始县教育体育局', NULL, NULL, NULL, '河南省', '郑州市', '固始县', '河南省 郑州市 固始县', '<p style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LETTER-SPACING: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt">河南海隆工程咨询有限公司受固始县教育体育局的委托，对固始县慈济高中实验楼及国机励志学校分校一期工程（景观）建设项目进行公开招标，已于2019年1月29日在《河南省政府采购网》、《河南省电子招标投标公共服务平台》、《全国公共资源交易平台（河南省•固始县）》上发布了招标公告。现对该项目发布变更公告：</font></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LETTER-SPACING: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt"><b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">一、</span></b><b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">原招标公告中：</span></b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black">“</span><b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">四、投标人资格要求</span></b></font></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LETTER-SPACING: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">2</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">、资质要求：</span></font></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LETTER-SPACING: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial"><span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">施工1标：应具备建筑工程施工总承包贰级以上（含贰级）资质；具备有效的安全生产许可证。拟派项目经理应具备建筑工程专业贰级以上（含贰级）注册建造师证书，具有有效的安全生产考核合格证，且未担任其他在建工程项目的项目经理，出具无在建项目承诺书。</span></span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LETTER-SPACING: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial"><span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">施工2标：应同时具备建筑工程及市政公用工程施工总承包贰级以上（含贰级）资质；具备有效的安全生产许可证。拟派项目经理应具备建筑工程或市政公用工程专业贰级以上（含贰级）注册建造师证书，具有有效的安全生产考核合格证，且未担任其他在建工程项目的项目经理，出具无在建项目承诺书。”</span></span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LETTER-SPACING: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 21.1pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt"><b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">现变更为：</span></b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">“</span><b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">四、投标人资格要求</span></b></font></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LETTER-SPACING: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">2</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">、资质要求：</span></font></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LETTER-SPACING: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial"><span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">施工1标：应具备建筑工程施工总承包叁级以上（含叁级）资质；具备有效的安全生产许可证。拟派项目经理应具备建筑工程专业贰级以上（含贰级）注册建造师证书，具有有效的安全生产考核合格证，且未担任其他在建工程项目的项目经理，出具无在建项目承诺书。</span></span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LETTER-SPACING: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial"><span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt">施工2标：应同时具备建筑工程及市政公用工程施工总承包叁级以上（含叁级）资质；具备有效的安全生产许可证。拟派项目经理应具备建筑工程及市政公用工程专业贰级以上（含贰级）注册建造师证书，具有有效的安全生产考核合格证，且未担任其他在建工程项目的项目经理，出具无在建项目承诺书。”</span></span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LETTER-SPACING: normal; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial"><span><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt">二、招标文件中相对应部分依照此变更做相应更改。</span></b></span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PA